{"tid":2410342,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"政府食市結論 懶人包","createTime":"2021-02-16T13:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T15:13:46.000Z","uid":80564,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea724cc9c69174690e025d8028c470889ef1d0c","tid":2410342,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:48:15.000Z","msg":"結論 懶人包<br />\n👉🏼食肆及處所必須全日要求顧客使用「安心出行」，或登記顧客資料<br />\n（姓名、聯絡電話等）<br />\n👉🏼可以4人一枱<br />\n👉🏼員工每2星期檢測一次<br />\n👉🏼食肆延長至晚上十時<br />\n👉🏼未有採取相關措施，則可能被要求停業、或要求縮短營業時間至下午5:59分，2人一枱；為期3、7、14天<br />\n第二個方案<br />\n👉🏼不需要食肆及處所必須全日要求顧客使用「安心出行」，或登記顧客資料<br />\n（姓名、聯絡電話等）<br />\n👉🏼只可以2人一枱<br />\n👉🏼食肆只可營業到六時（外賣都不可以）<br />\n👉🏼不需要安排員工檢測<br />\n<br />\n衝著黃店而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37f9c6a177234b53046227ec1525703f9c96345","tid":2410342,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:49:58.000Z","msg":"有無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659c671fe0ce40b5b4921c7f5ba28d7fc541ff23","tid":2410342,"uid":54528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T13:53:32.000Z","msg":"邊個契弟諗埋呢d弱智方案<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36101c1ee6a720568e72d0be5fa5cc0d4512900c","tid":2410342,"uid":392566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:07:44.000Z","msg":"欺人太甚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b1fcab5f0579966e70776daed22f692560c1631","tid":2410342,"uid":365076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"邊個諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1439b1d18b7b8aa031d25b6d35df685f9389b346","tid":2410342,"uid":80564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc